'''Nectar pearls''' were round, gray containers which were used to carry [[kete nectar]]. The [[Kete]]s on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon of Endor]] used nectar pearls to carry the nectar back to their hive. The shape of the pearls allowed the Ketes to conveniently store the pearls within storehouses inside their [[Kete hive|hive]]. During the [[stranglethorn crisis]], the two [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]], [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] and [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]] obtained a nectar pearl from the Kete hive because of the importance of kete nectar in the antidote for [[plant growth formula]].

